<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.6">
<l>cattira mēntit taṉiyoru māṇiyā</l>
<l>yuttara vētiyil niṉṟavo ruvaṉai</l>
<l>kattiri yarkāṇak kāṇimuṟ ṟumkoṇṭa</l>
<l>pattirā kāraṉ puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">pāraḷan tāṉeṉ puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He with auspicious features, holding an umbrella</l>
<l>as a unique brahmacāri, while the warriors watched</l>
<l>the one [Mahābali] who stood at the northern altar,</l>
<l>who took the whole land will embrace [me] from behind.</l>
<l>He who measured the earth will embrace me from behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
